  <brief_title>Effect of Lidocaine in Antiarrhythmic Dosage on Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Supratentorial Craniotomy Dysfunction in Supratentorial Craniotomy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
