  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of lidocaine in antiarrhythmic dosage
      on postoperative cognitive dysfunction in supratentorial craniotomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
